name: Danke Handcarved Rubber Stamp
description:
TAKE NOTE: The stamp is made to order and will vary slightly including the color.


Danke rubber stamp is made with Staedtler Mars vinyl erasers and carved by Mall with her vintage Speedball linoleum cutter. This rubber stamp measures 2.5" inches X 0.9" inch. Kirkusy font stamp!

It is unmounted and can be used with any ink pad. Perfect for envelopes, boxes, packages, fabrics, scrapbook, more projects!

It will be packed in a plastic sleeve protection in a bubble envelope.


CLEANING:
Some rubber stamp inks will come off your stamp with only water and mild soap. Then pat them gently on a soft paper towel or rag and dry them completely before storing. NEVER USE SOLVENT AND BABY WIPES. NEVER RUB / WIPE and don't soak your stamps in water unless your stamps will not ruin.

STORAGE:
Don't stack the stamps on top of each other because they could stick to each other. Store your unmounted stamps in any plastic cases so they won't get dusty. Avoid exposure to excessive heat, this will damage the rubber.

MOUNTING:
If it's hard to stamp your unmounted rubber stamps, please use a mounting block or acrylic block or wood block. Try to find them in the art / craft stores there or if you have unused wood blocks. Please read and visit this site about mounting the stamp http://www.atlasquest.com/tutorials/carving/mounting.html


All rubber stamp designs are made by copyright  May Ann Licudine aka Mall. Do not steal nor copy her designs, they are not for commercial use. Thank you!

name: Kirkus Pocket Mirror
description:
Please let me know what you choose one. 

This is a new 2.25 inch (5.7cm) Kirkus pocket mirror based on my illustration. Please check my portfolio: www.mayannlicudine.com and my blog: http://nnayam.blogspot.com/

It's adorably perfect for your pocket / purse and bag. It's easy to check yourself out in anywhere! This will also be a perfect present for your boyfriend, hubby, friend/s, family members, love ones and circus lovers! You can also use them all at once that can catch anybody's eyes.

Please see different colors and styles of Kirkus pocket mirrors, that would suit your characteristic or even your emotions from day to day. Enjoy!

All designs are made by copyright  May Ann Licudine aka Mall. Do not steal nor copy her designs, they are not for commercial use. Thank you!
